    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Game in which one player is blindfolded, and tries to catch and identify any one of the others, who, on their part, push him about, and make sport with him.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
